quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,"By the fig and the olive;",footnotes:182770:1
  95,2,"and by the Mount Sinai,",footnotes:182031:1
  95,3,"and by this city (of Makkah), a haven of peace:"
  95,4,"surely We created man in the best mould;",footnotes:182771:1
  95,5,"then We reverted him to the lowest of the low,",footnotes:182772:1
  95,6,"except those who have faith and do righteous deeds. Theirs is a never ending reward.",footnotes:182773:1
  95,7,"Who, then, can give the lie to you, (O Prophet), about the Reward and the Punishment?",footnotes:182774:1
  95,8,"Is not Allah the Greatest of all sovereigns?",footnotes:182775:1
